<div class="index-section">

  <h1>Books I've written</h1>

  <h4><a href="http://book.mixu.net/css/">Learn CSS Layout the pedantic way</a> (2015)</h4>

  <p>Walks you through every major concept in CSS layout, without trying to simplify away the underlying mechanisms described in the CSS 2.1 and flexbox specs.</p>

  <p>Alternative formats: <a href="https://github.com/mixu/cssbook">Github</a>, <a href="http://book.mixu.net/css/single-page.html">Single HTML page</a>, <a href="http://www.printfriendly.com/print/v2?url=http://book.mixu.net/css/single-page.html">PDF</a>.

  </p><h4><a href="http://book.mixu.net/distsys/">Distributed systems: for fun and profit</a> (2013)</h4>

  <p>An introduction to distributed systems.</p>

  <p>Alternative formats: <a href="https://github.com/mixu/distsysbook">Github</a>, <a href="http://book.mixu.net/distsys/single-page.html">Single HTML page</a>, <a href="http://book.mixu.net/distsys/mixu-distributed-systems-book.mobi">Kindle .mobi</a>, <a href="http://www.printfriendly.com/print/v2?url=http://book.mixu.net/distsys/ebook.html">PDF</a> and <a href="http://book.mixu.net/distsys/mixu-distributed-systems-book.epub">.epub</a>.</p>

  <h4><a href="http://singlepageappbook.com/">Single page apps in depth</a> (2013)</h4>

  <p>Single page web apps and good practices around writing single page apps.</p>

  <p>Alternative formats: <a href="https://github.com/mixu/singlepageappbook">Github</a>, <a href="http://singlepageappbook.com/single-page.html">Single HTML page</a>, <a href="http://singlepageappbook.com/mixu-single-page-apps.mobi">Kindle .mobi</a>, <a href="http://www.printfriendly.com/print/v2?url=http://singlepageappbook.com/single-page.html">PDF</a> and <a href="http://singlepageappbook.com/mixu-single-page-apps.epub">.epub</a>.</p>

  <h4><a href="http://book.mixu.net/node/">Mixu's Node book</a> (2012)</h4>

  <p>Node.js patterns and core libraries, JS gotchas, control flow and Socket.io.</p>

  <p>Alternative formats: <a href="http://book.mixu.net/node/single.html">Single HTML page</a>, <a href="http://book.mixu.net/node/mixu-node-book.mobi">Kindle .mobi</a>, <a href="http://www.printfriendly.com/print/v2?url=http://book.mixu.net/node/single.html">PDF</a> and <a href="http://book.mixu.net/node/mixu-node-book.epub">.epub</a>.</p>

